responseText: You did well, my friend.  Unfortunately, the script is written in an ancient dialect that I do not recognize.  The abjad I see appears Vaelune but I concede that I am unable discern the grapheme.  Fortunately for us, my auxiliaries are excellent philogists and can help us decipher the script.  If you can, my friend, will you take these rubbings to my associates, gather their notes, and return them to me?
name: DD_SQ_0011_HistorianQatakijal_11_Response
